  "body": "Users of the `WaitFor` function would expect the close of the \"done\" channel should terminate the [WaitFor](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/staging/src/k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/wait/wait.go#L385). We should change the function to align to users' expectation.\r\n\r\nWe should document what the `done` channel does.\r\n\r\nThis is a behavior change, to be cautious, we should add a release note claiming breaking change.\r\n\r\n/kind bug",
